<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 9800 - 18 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO-14618 AND RTLO-16618
        SERIES - REMOVE - SHIFTER HOUSING
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="1">
        <title>SHIFTER HOUSING</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>For models equipped with an Oil Pump and/or Cooler Assemblies, make sure to disconnect the lube
                    line at the fitting on the shifter housing before doing the following instructions.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <para>Remove the retaining bolts (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1301925">Figure 25</hotlnk>). Jar the top to break the gasket seal and lift the shifter
            housing from the transmission case. Remove the gasket.
        </para>
        <figure id="f1301925" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1301925" filename="../figg13/g1301925.webp" type="webp" resolution="72"/>
            <caption>Figure 25. Remove Retaining Bolts</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
